<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ subject|default('Thank you for browsing our catalogue online') }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f3f4f6; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#374151;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f3f4f6; padding:24px 12px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="max-width:970px; background-color:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#374151;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">Dear <span style="font-style:italic;">{{ client_name|default("[Client's name]") }},</span></p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">Thank you for your catalogue request. I have mailed you a copy of our new 2026 catalogue in the post and you should receive it shortly.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#374151;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">For your information, we’ve been operating in Australia for over 30 years. Our mission is to offer the best service and the highest quality products at competitive prices. We manufacture in Australia and hold unparalleled stock levels, which enables us to provide the fastest lead times in the industry.</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">We welcome you to view our entire range in our world class showrooms in Sydney, Melbourne, and Brisbane or take our <a href="{{ showroom_tour_url|default('http://54.252.147.60:8089/contact-us') }}" style="color:#255793; text-decoration:underline;">showroom virtual tour</a> from the comfort of your own home or current office.</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">Please browse through some of our recent <a href="{{ projects_url|default('https://www.krost.com.au/Projects') }}" style="color:#255793; text-decoration:underline;">projects</a>.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#374151;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">Should you have any questions please don’t hesitate to call us on {{ sales_phone|default('02 9557 3055') }} or email at <span style="text-decoration:underline;">{{ sales_email|default('sales@krost.com.au') }}</span>.</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">Kind regards,</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:1.7;">The Krost Team</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
